    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. This nourishing curry is big on flavour, not on effort. You'll simmer juicy chicken meatballs in a rich coconut masala sauce with courgette and a squeeze of fresh lime. Ready in 20, this is feel-good comfort at its finest.",
